WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.068 --> 00:00:02.503
WHAT OF WE DO LIKE
A LITTLE SCRIMMAGE?

00:00:02.536 --> 00:00:04.071
ADAM, YOU BE THE FIREE...

00:00:04.104 --> 00:00:06.373
- THAT DOESN'T MAKE MUCH SENSE,
KINDA THE TOP GUN.

00:00:06.406 --> 00:00:08.809
- AND I WILL BE
THE FIRER, OKAY.

00:00:08.842 --> 00:00:11.778
AND NO MATTER WHAT THIS GUY SAYS
OR THROWS MY WAY, YOU KNOW,

00:00:11.812 --> 00:00:15.048
I'LL JUST POWER THROUGH
AND I'LL FIRE THE GUY, OKAY?

00:00:15.082 --> 00:00:16.416
IT'S REAL EASY.
ARE YOU READY?

00:00:16.450 --> 00:00:18.919
- I'M READY.
- OKAY. LET'S GET TO IT.

00:00:18.952 --> 00:00:24.691
ADAM, I'M SORRY TO SAY THIS,
BUT WE GOT TO LET YOU GO, BUD.

00:00:27.661 --> 00:00:29.363
- YOU'RE FIRING ME?

00:00:29.396 --> 00:00:34.101
I WORK HERE FOR 60 YEARS
BUILDING THIS COMPANY

00:00:34.134 --> 00:00:37.504
FROM THE GROUND UP,
AND YOU FIRING ME?

00:00:37.538 --> 00:00:38.839
- SORRY, DUDE.

00:00:38.872 --> 00:00:43.310
- I AIN'T GOING OUT
LIKE NO BITCH, YOU BITCH.

00:00:43.343 --> 00:00:44.645
- ANDERS, YOU HEARD ANYTHING?

00:00:44.678 --> 00:00:47.014
I CAN'T LOSE MY JOB,
YOU UNDERSTAND?

00:00:47.047 --> 00:00:48.782
I AIN'T GOING BACK
TO SUBSTITUTE TEACHING.

00:00:48.815 --> 00:00:50.951
- MONTEZ, MY EYES
ARE BURNING RIGHT NOW.

00:00:50.984 --> 00:00:51.885
COME ON.

00:00:51.919 --> 00:00:54.721
- YOU KIDS GOT NO SHAME,
NO DECENCY.

00:00:54.755 --> 00:00:56.623
THANKS FOR THIS APRON, MAN.

00:00:56.657 --> 00:01:00.127
- YOU GOT A .44 MAGNUM
POINTED AT YOUR HEAD.

00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:02.763
WHAT THE [bleep]
ARE YOU DOING?

00:01:02.796 --> 00:01:07.734
YOU FIRE ME, I'LL KILL YOU
AND EVERYBODY IN HERE.

00:01:07.768 --> 00:01:10.270
- OH, DO WHAT HE SAYS, BLAKE.

00:01:10.304 --> 00:01:12.105
- YOU REALLY THINK
I'M THAT STUPID?

00:01:12.139 --> 00:01:13.941
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

00:01:13.974 --> 00:01:18.846
- CHECK THE GUN, HOTSHOT.

00:01:18.879 --> 00:01:20.547
- VERY CLEVER.

00:01:20.581 --> 00:01:22.850
VERY CLEVER.

00:01:22.883 --> 00:01:24.651
YOU TAKE THE BULLETS
OUT OF MY GUN.

00:01:24.685 --> 00:01:25.786
- YEAH.

00:01:25.819 --> 00:01:28.722
- BUT LET'S SEE IF YOU CAN
TAKE THE BULLETS

00:01:28.755 --> 00:01:32.826
OUT OF THIS BUTTERFLY KNIFE.

00:01:35.996 --> 00:01:38.699
- JILLIAN, GO AHEAD AND GIVE
THIS GUY A CIGARETTE,

00:01:38.732 --> 00:01:40.834
'CAUSE I'M ABOUT
TO LIGHT HIM UP.

00:01:43.170 --> 00:01:44.104
- ARE THOSE SUNGLASSES?

00:01:44.104 --> 00:01:47.107
- YEAH, SUNGLASSES.
- COOL.

00:01:47.107 --> 00:01:48.842
- FOR MY FLAMETHROWER.

00:01:48.876 --> 00:01:50.811
- NO, NO.

00:01:50.844 --> 00:01:55.115
- YOU'RE FIRED.
- NO!

00:01:55.115 --> 00:01:56.149
- YOU'RE SO FIRED.

00:01:56.183 --> 00:01:58.218
- [screaming]

00:02:03.257 --> 00:02:06.260
- OOH! OOH! OOH!

00:02:06.293 --> 00:02:09.830
- [still screaming]

00:02:11.665 --> 00:02:12.799
- AND HE'S FIRED.

00:02:12.833 --> 00:02:14.368
- AND I'M FIRED.
- AND HE'S FIRED.

00:02:14.401 --> 00:02:16.503
- THAT WAS VERY INFORMATIVE.
- THANK YOU.

